ournal.net/c28.htm \"Introduction\"] to ''Critique 28/29: The Ideas of Victor Serge: a Life as a Work of Art'' (Edited by Susan Weissman) (Retrieved March 14, 2007.)\n\n{{Authority control}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Serge, Victor}}\n[[Category:1890 births]]\n[[Category:1947 deaths]]\n[[Category:People from Brussels]]\n[[Category:Anarcho-communists]]\n[[Category:Illegalists]]\n[[Category:Comintern people]]\n[[Category:French people of Russian descent]]\n[[Category:Left communists]]\n[[Category:Marxist journalists]]\n[[Category:Russian\u2013French translators]]\n[[Category:Individualist anarchists]]\n[[Category:Russian anarchists]]\n[[Category:Russian communists]]\n[[Category:Russian socialists]]\n[[Category:Russian historians]]\n[[Category:Russian revolutionaries]]\n[[Category:Russian people of Polish descent]]\n[[Category:Soviet expellees]]\n[[Category:Soviet anarchists]]\n[[Category:Soviet Trotskyists]]\n[[Category:Communist writers]]\n[[Category:20th-century historians]]\n[[Category:Soviet emigrants to France]]\n[[Category:Soviet emigrants to Belgium]]\n[[Category:Soviet emigrants to Mexico]]\n[[Category:Left Opposition]]\n", "name_user": "Grinchitude", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eIn Mexico:Corrected typo; changed \"trucking\" to \"truckling\"", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victor_Serge"}
